  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetPerformanceHintCpu</TypeRef> method returns the specified CPU performance hint for this index attribute.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[PerformanceHint GetPerformanceHintCpu() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="PerformanceHint">
        The CPU-side performance hint configured for this attribute.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
